Package com.github.tadukoo.util.view.components

Contains components that provide extra customizations via Tadukoo Look & Feel (e.g. ShapeInfo) and/or methods to make it easier to deal with the components (e.g. the add row methods in TadukooTable)
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    TadukooButton
    Tadukoo Button is an extension of JButton that allows for specifying more parameters that can be used in Tadukoo Look & Feel, such as ShapeInfo.
    TadukooButton.TadukooButtonBuilder
    Builder to be used to create a TadukooButton.
    TadukooTable
    Tadukoo Table is an extension of JScrollPane that contains a JTable.
    TadukooTable.TadukooTableBuilder
    Builder to be used to create a TadukooTable.
